  "2026-06-14T21:35:22.202Z",claude-code-agent,"Dispatched 3 parallel lane sub-agents on branch test/all-source-100pct-coverage-gate (off main). Full-surface baseline (thresholds-disabled probe): 96.07% stmts / 89.55% branches / 96.46% funcs / 96.33% lines. Gap map: Lane A 99 src files <100 (branch-heavy: register-mutation B70.98 worst), Lane B 22 files (beads/todos runtime-loader L76/B53 worst), Lane C 26 scripts (4 still at 0%: gen-package-runtime-loaders, gen-plugin-mcp-wrappers, prepare-build-cache, finalize-build; run-release-pipeline L45/B31 worst). Each agent claims its lane chore (pm-krwu/pm-6tch/pm-f2ne) and documents evidence there. Agents instructed: new specs in tests/unit/lane-*/ only (root at 120 cap), SKIP_BUILD, no vitest.config edits, v8/c8-ignore only for provably-unreachable defensive branches w/ justification."
